---
title: BBQ Chicken and Bacon Pizzas with Garden Salad
description: These pizzas are a breeze to whip up, with pre-made dough that is as easy as pie to roll out! The sweet and smoky BBQ sauce base is sure to be a hit with the whole family!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pizzas-au-poulet-bbq-et-au-bacon-4c2bf2bc.jpg
